# Environment Variables Configuration

## Frontend (.env at root)
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000

## Backend (backend/.env)

# Server Configuration
PORT=5000
FRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:5173

# Email Configuration (Gmail example)
EMAIL_USER=your-email@gmail.com
EMAIL_PASS=your-app-password-16-chars

# Security
JWT_SECRET=your-super-secret-jwt-key-minimum-32-characters-change-in-production

# Database
DATABASE_URL="file:./dev.db"

# Optional: Email service provider
# EMAIL_SERVICE=gmail

## Production Example

### Frontend Production (.env.production)
VITE_API_URL=https://api.yourdomain.com

### Backend Production (.env.production)
PORT=5000
FRONTEND_URL=https://yourdomain.com
EMAIL_USER=noreply@yourdomain.com
EMAIL_PASS=production-app-password
JWT_SECRET=production-secret-key-64-characters-or-more-for-maximum-security-AES256
DATABASE_URL="postgresql://user:password@localhost:5432/ecertificate?schema=public"
